Invocation Name: s. f. m. live stream
des:
Live stream of SFM Streek Radio from the Garden Route in South Africa. Visit SFM Streek Radio at: https://www.sfmstreek.com/.

Top Tip: To launch this skill, create a routine in the Alexa app and add your preferred phrase to launch this station. Pick your own launch phrase and point it to "S. F. M." Radio Try it out!

Terms of use:
The SFM presenters broadcast in the Afrikaans language.
This skill or parts of it may be discontinued at any time and is provided without any guarantees.
The skill might contain errors and might stop to function for reasons outside of the control of the developer. You use this skill at your own risk. 
The developer is not affiliated with the radio station in any way and created this skill purely for the enjoyment of listening to the station. This skill is therefore an unofficial streaming channel for fans of the station.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
